data.description: Wonderful 3 bedroom (all on the upper level) Rambler boasts the following wonderful features: Three bedrooms on the main level with hardwood floors - Vinyl Windows - huge Family Room in the lower level - A Game Room that is an amazing spot to hang out as it has permanent carpet (but no permanent ceiling, so it is not included in the finished sq. ft.) - An office area or potential 4th bedroom that needs an egress window (currently used for storage) - Huge Laundry/Mechanical area offers additional storage space as well - Large, fenced in back yard with an 8x8 Storage shed - Spacious two car attached garage has room for two cars plus storage. Closing can be flexible on this amazing home - schedule your showing today!
